{"word":"Water","slug":"water","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Water</b> Creation of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=148&verse=5'>Psa 148:5</a><br/> Covered the whole earth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=9'>Gen 1:9</a><br/> Daily allowance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4&verse=11'>Eze 4:11</a><br/> City waterworks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=20'>2Ki 20:20</a><br/> Vision of, by Ezekiel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=5'>Eze 47:5</a><br/> Of separation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=22'>Num 19:22</a><br/> Libation of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=6'>1Sa 7:6</a><br/> Irrigation with<br/> <a href='S:Irrigation'>Irrigation</a><br/> Miraculously supplied:<br/> - To the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=1'>Exo 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=6'>Exo 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=11'>Num 20:11</a> <br/> - To Samson<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=15&verse=19'>Jdg 15:19</a> <br/> - To Jehoshaphat's army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=20'>2Ki 3:20</a> <br/> Purified by Elisha<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=22'>2Ki 2:22</a><br/> Red Sea divided<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=22'>Exo 14:22</a><br/> The river Jordan divided<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=3&verse=17'>Jos 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=8'>2Ki 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=14'>2Ki 2:14</a><br/> Jesus walks on<br/> <a h